{"tid":559791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美臣頭傷嚴重終退役","createTime":"2018-02-13T13:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T11:14:15.000Z","uid":20916,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"77e72a83fe9faf98b92b27338407b3491cd9c07b","tid":559791,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=juZNQ8TWd%2FZKTWwpyWEy8ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4df9f5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】侯城於周二宣佈，26歲中場賴恩美臣因為去年的嚴重頭部受傷，決定提早高掛球靴。<br />\n<br />\n「球會十分遺憾的宣佈，由於在2017年1月22日頭部受傷，賴恩美臣（Ryan Mason）決定現在退役。美臣已尋求了多位世界著名神經科及神經外科專家的意見，他們都建議美臣，不應該重返球場。」侯城於聲明中表示。<br />\n<br />\n賴恩美臣同時透過這份聲明，感激侯城在過去12個月對他在康復道路上的支持。於熱刺出道的他，在去年英超為老虎鬥車路士時，被對方中堅加利卡希爾撞至頭骨爆裂，之後立即被送到醫院，而且留院8天。<br />\n<br />\n在去年10月，他曾表示計劃復出：「體能上，我沒有問題，可是我的頭骨仍然需要時間去復原，希望到復原的那天，我可以有足夠的體能，立即回到球場比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n侯城現時於英冠以31戰29分排尾4，護級水深火熱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1148fb03ef9831d29f71c36c602b9cdd555b62d","tid":559791,"uid":8588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71637f27244f7cf244cb3ad2866a828d9810308","tid":559791,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3159a10a938037fd8a416652ab5c94bfab9331e9","tid":559791,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"rip\\丨／"},{"pid":"58ec0f6b4e86951e10c9fdc8b59831cddd7e6e41","tid":559791,"uid":20916,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b71637f27244f7cf244cb3ad2866a828d9810308","tid":559791,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":